title: Miller: Breaking up is easy to do, just hard to explain for Dodgers, Mattingly
text: Miller: Breaking up is easy to do, just hard to explain for Dodgers, Mattingly Oct. 22, 2015 Updated 8:21 p.m. 1 of 1 Dodger president of baseball operations Andrew Friedman insisted Thursday he expected Don Mattingly to return as manager in 2016 before their amicable conversations led to a parting of the ways. RICHARD VOGEL, THE ASSOCIATED PRESS Dodger president of baseball operations Andrew Friedman insisted Thursday he expected Don Mattingly to return as manager in 2016 before their amicable conversations led to a parting of the ways.
